Dia akan menjadi orang lain
Wanita di depan tuan muda saya?

434
00:31:42,044 --> 00:31:43,688
Apa yang bisa saya lakukan?

435
00:31:43,788 --> 00:31:45,613
Jika Anda tidak dapat melakukan apa-apa, siapa yang bisa?

436
00:31:45,614 --> 00:31:50,827
Hal ini dilarang untuk pelacur pemula untuk
pergi keluar sebelum mereka mengangkat rambut mereka.

437
00:31:51,139 --> 00:31:53,569
Ini aturan! Apa yang bisa saya lakukan?

438
00:31:55,458 --> 00:31:57,596
Apakah dia memberikan pesan untuk saya?

439
00:32:11,448 --> 00:32:13,586
Tari adalah puisi dalam gerak.

440
00:32:13,587 --> 00:32:16,999
Seorang penari harus mampu berbicara
seribu kata dengan tubuhnya.

441
00:32:18,155 --> 00:32:20,905
Dengan tubuhnya, dia harus
mampu menarik ribuan skenario.

442
00:32:21,474 --> 00:32:24,939
Seorang penari yang baik menggunakan tangan dan kakinya

443
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:30,311
dan tubuhnya untuk tidak hanya memimpin
orang ke kebun,

444
00:32:31,316 --> 00:32:33,541
tapi dia bisa mengubah dirinya sendiri
menjadi seorang anak menangkap kupu-kupu,

445
00:32:34,415 --> 00:32:39,579
atau orang tua kesepian yang berjuang
dengan kepahitan dan kesepian.

446
00:32:48,655 --> 00:32:51,872
Berdiri di atas blok dan ambil tali!

447
00:33:01,489 --> 00:33:03,575
Menendang blok jauhnya!

448
00:33:04,353 --> 00:33:08,185
- Apa?
- Aku berkata menendang blok jauhnya!

449
00:33:20,713 --> 00:33:24,495
- Nyonya!
- Lengan kami akan ditarik off!

450
00:33:25,302 --> 00:33:27,294
Apakah Anda tidak melakukan apa yang diperintahkan!

451
00:34:03,294 --> 00:34:06,617
- Geum-Choon.
- Ya, Nyonya?

452
00:34:22,339 --> 00:34:25,300
Bersantai kaki Anda!

453
00:34:54,159 --> 00:34:57,275
Dia menggantung mereka terbalik
turun sepanjang hari?

454
00:34:57,932 --> 00:35:01,539
- Apakah Anda yakin?
- Tentu saja!

455
00:35:03,035 --> 00:35:07,853
Aku tidak tahu apa yang sedang dipikirkannya!
Mungkin dia berpikir mereka laundry!

456
00:35:09,021 --> 00:35:12,247
Dara konyol! Beraninya kau tertawa?

457
00:35:12,625 --> 00:35:14,800
Bagaimana Anda bisa tertawa pada saat seperti ini?

458
00:35:15,700 --> 00:35:17,182
Mi ... Nyonya!

459
00:35:17,597 --> 00:35:20,227
Apakah mungkin mereka ingin
untuk melakukan tarian itu?

460
00:35:20,828 --> 00:35:23,216
Akankah mereka melakukan Crane Dance?

461
00:35:35,070 --> 00:35:38,053
Mengapa Anda terlihat begitu khawatir?

462
00:35:39,798 --> 00:35:44,185
Kami telah melakukan
Derek Dance berkali-kali.

463
00:35:46,947 --> 00:35:51,878
Tarian ... The Crane Dance
bahwa Baek-Moo tahu ...

464
00:35:52,416 --> 00:35:54,903
berbeda dari Dance Derek kami.

465
00:35:55,711 --> 00:35:57,811
Berbeda dalam hal apa?

466
00:35:59,512 --> 00:36:04,401
Dulu, ada seorang penari
bernama Ja Dong-Matahari.

467
00:36:04,402 --> 00:36:09,651
Dia memiliki semacam bakat yang muncul
sekali setiap seratus, tidak, seribu tahun.

468
00:36:11,146 --> 00:36:15,160
Dia adalah orang yang mengajarkan

469
00:36:15,791 --> 00:36:18,889
Baek-Moo dan saya sendiri bagaimana menari.

470
00:36:20,524 --> 00:36:25,717
Dia adalah salah satu yang
koreografer Crane Dance.

471
00:36:27,749 --> 00:36:33,599
Tidak seorang pun yang pernah melihat
Crane Dance dilakukan.

472
00:36:44,444 --> 00:36:48,232
<i> Ini adalah tarian indah </ i>

473
00:36:49,041 --> 00:36:52,198
<i> penari menjadi crane,
dan derek menjadi penari. </ i>

474
00:36:52,538 --> 00:36:56,353
<i> Bila Anda mengharapkan kaki menjadi
di udara, mereka berada di tanah. </ i>

475
00:36:56,786 --> 00:37:01,284
<i> Dan ketika Anda berpikir mereka
di tanah, mereka berada di udara. </ i>

476
00:37:03,886 --> 00:37:09,447
<i> derek datang turun ke bumi
hanya untuk memenuhi kebutuhan fisiknya. </ i>

477
00:37:10,683 --> 00:37:16,674
<i> Tapi itu adalah takdir crane ke tempat
keinginan dan impian di langit. </ i>

478
00:37:17,965 --> 00:37:23,694
<i> naik, naik dan naik lagi
ke langit. </ i>

479
00:37:28,763 --> 00:37:33,442
Ini adalah tarian yang luar biasa dan indah.

480
00:37:35,267 --> 00:37:40,581
Tidak bisa tari lain
dibandingkan dengan Crane Dance.

481
00:37:41,679 --> 00:37:44,681
Apakah ada buku yang mencatat
gerakan tarian ini?

482
00:37:47,125 --> 00:37:48,292
Ada.

483
00:37:48,896 --> 00:37:51,832
Tolong beri saya buku itu.

484
00:37:52,244 --> 00:37:54,670
Aku akan belajar gerakan dengan hati ...

485
00:37:54,828 --> 00:37:57,922
Buku yang mencatat tari guru saya ...

486
00:37:58,564 --> 00:38:03,163
menyembunyikan dirinya pada saat itu
meninggalnya guru saya.

487
00:38:04,193 --> 00:38:07,676
Tapi ... Anda mengatakan ada sebuah buku?

488
00:38:10,884 --> 00:38:16,262
Buku ini tidak lain adalah
Nyonya Song-Do rombongan, Baek-Moo.

489
00:38:19,748 --> 00:38:22,593
Sebelum guru saya meninggal,

490
00:38:23,781 --> 00:38:27,333
ia lulus pada tari
hanya untuk Baek-Moo.

491
00:38:32,268 --> 00:38:35,540
Jika intuisi saya benar
dan anak perempuan Baek-Moo kita belajar tarian itu,

492
00:38:35,541 --> 00:38:38,232
itu tidak hanya akan menjadi menteri

493
00:38:39,035 --> 00:38:42,106
tapi bahkan Yang Mulia tidak akan
mampu mengubah matanya pergi.

494
00:38:43,555 --> 00:38:48,077
Lalu ... kita akan kalah?

495
00:38:48,649 --> 00:38:52,047
- Belum tentu!
- Nyonya ...!

496
00:38:52,048 --> 00:38:55,220
Kita harus mengubah mata mereka pergi.

497
00:38:55,660 --> 00:38:58,567
Untuk tempat yang lebih kuat dari mereka
apresiasi seni!

498
00:39:18,643 --> 00:39:21,482
Pandangan ini benar-benar luar biasa!

499
00:39:23,413 --> 00:39:26,223
Indah, hanya indah!

500
00:39:26,864 --> 00:39:31,927
- Apakah semua menteri penting di sini?
- Tentu saja.

501
00:39:45,039 --> 00:39:48,234
Aku tidak tahu bahwa
Yang Mulia akan menghadiri.

502
00:39:48,235 --> 00:39:51,789
Mengapa? Haruskah saya tidak berada di sini?

503
00:39:53,734 --> 00:39:55,148
Itu tidak apa ...

504
00:39:55,606 --> 00:39:57,869
Saya mendengar berita dari Tuhan Byuk Gae-Soo.

505
00:39:57,870 --> 00:40:01,784
Jika pelacur istana
membuang perjamuan,

506
00:40:02,168 --> 00:40:05,695
Saya sebagai Menteri Sumber Daya
tentu saja harus hadir.

507
00:40:08,123 --> 00:40:12,743
Mae-Hyang, Anda telah mengundang semua orang

508
00:40:12,744 ---> 00:40:15,769
from civil ministers to high ministers here!

509
00:40:16,461 ---> 00:40:20,673
The sphere of influence within your skirts
is as expansive as the Han River!

510
00:40:22,383 ---> 00:40:24,809
You are too kind, my Lord.

511
00:40:24,810 ---> 00:40:29,716
You must really be worried about
the competition with Baek-Moo!

512
00:40:31,525 ---> 00:40:35,691
Here here! It has been a long time!

513
00:40:38,255 ---> 00:40:40,582
Selamat Datang!

514
00:41:43,528 ---> 00:41:45,981
Bagaimana?

515
00:41:45,982 ---> 00:41:48,133
They are quite skilled.

516
00:41:48,134 ---> 00:41:51,386
We are honored by your words.

517
00:41:55,126 ---> 00:42:00,670
Should you find any girl to
your liking, please let me know.

518
00:42:01,708 ---> 00:42:05,073
I shall instruct her to serve you
with her utmost dedication.

519
00:42:06,826 ---> 00:42:10,011
We know your appreciation and
knowledge of the arts is great.

520
00:42:10,272 ---> 00:42:13,257
Thus we are unsatisfied by
your sparse words of review.

521
00:42:13,840 ---> 00:42:15,783
Please be more specific in your criticism.

522
00:42:16,086 ---> 00:42:19,371
Then those girls can continue
what they do well,

523
00:42:19,577 ---> 00:42:24,741
and improve what they don't do well
for a much better performance.

524
00:42:26,045 ---> 00:42:28,205
Mari kita lihat ...

525
00:42:35,328 ---> 00:42:40,731
Mae-Hyang, for the next performance,
you should acquire another boat.

526
00:42:42,417 ---> 00:42:47,077
The most eye-catching thing at today's
performance was the boat, was it not?

527
00:42:48,749 ---> 00:42:51,464
I have seen this Sunyoorak dance many times,

528
00:42:51,753 ---> 00:42:55,128
but I have never seen such
an excellent boat.

529
00:42:56,357 ---> 00:42:59,827
So, you should make another boat.

530
00:43:00,704 ---> 00:43:03,255
The dance is all the same.

531
00:43:03,925 ---> 00:43:07,350
It's a ritual dance
and cannot be helped.

532
00:43:08,261 ---> 00:43:12,249
Please wait until the next banquet.

533
00:43:12,536 ---> 00:43:17,746
There may just be a dancer who
may surprise all of us with her talents!

534
00:43:23,643 ---> 00:43:26,027
Lower your right arm!

535
00:43:32,463 ---> 00:43:35,626
Raise your right arm!

536
00:43:41,962 ---> 00:43:45,096
The little smile!

537
00:43:55,230 ---> 00:43:59,576
- Raise your right arm!
- Raise your right arm!

538
00:45:25,963 ---> 00:45:29,862
You are supposed to be dancing,
not thrashing your knives around.

539
00:45:31,328 ---> 00:45:34,268
And your expression should be lovely.

540
00:45:38,947 ---> 00:45:41,191
You have practiced enough today.

541
00:45:41,672 ---> 00:45:44,976
I have told them to
prepare a fragrant bath for you.

542
00:45:44,977 ---> 00:45:48,149
Go and have a long soak.

543
00:45:48,150 ---> 00:45:51,062
It won't be long before
you raise your hair.

544
00:45:52,482 ---> 00:45:55,702
I do not wish to think about that.

545
00:45:55,703 ---> 00:45:58,123
You do not wish to raise your hair?

546
00:45:59,183 ---> 00:46:02,252
I prefer to think about my practice.

547
00:46:02,253 ---> 00:46:04,839
Stop talking and go have your bath.

548
00:46:05,822 ---> 00:46:08,779
The only thing we can depend on now
is Lord Byuk Gae-Soo's influence.

549
00:46:09,112 ---> 00:46:12,392
I do not want to use wiles.
I want to win fairly!

550
00:46:14,652 ---> 00:46:16,702
Silly wench!

551
00:46:17,689 ---> 00:46:21,392
I thought you were smart,
but how naive you are!

552
00:46:22,802 ---> 00:46:26,422
Talent and ability does not secure
you a seat of power in this world.

553
00:46:26,423 ---> 00:46:31,821
If that were not the case,
Baek-Moo would be here in my place.

554
00:46:34,151 ---> 00:46:37,563
No matter how, you must secure
the heart of a man in power.

555
00:46:38,833 ---> 00:46:41,275
Talent comes after that.

556
00:46:41,276 ---> 00:46:43,842
Mistress...!

557
00:46:45,476 ---> 00:46:47,636
Heed my words.

558
00:46:48,376 ---> 00:46:50,986
It is not the strong who survive,

559
00:46:50,987 ---> 00:46:54,109
but the survivor who is strong.

560
00:46:55,935 ---> 00:46:58,595
That is the way of the world.

561
00:47:16,843 ---> 00:47:20,613
<i>Straighten your body until it
is parallel to the ground.</i>

562
00:47:22,893 ---> 00:47:24,610
<i>Remove all tension from your body</i>

563
00:47:24,611 ---> 00:47:29,465
<i>and make your being as light
as the air and the wind.</i>

564
00:47:32,822 ---> 00:47:36,122
<i>Move your body like a breeze!</i>

565
00:47:40,103 ---> 00:47:42,463
<i>Stretch out your arms!</i>

566
00:47:44,108 ---> 00:47:47,168
<i>Bend your wrists!</i>

567
00:48:31,122 ---> 00:48:33,622
<i>Heed my words.</i>

568
00:48:33,923 ---> 00:48:37,012
<i>It is not the strong that survive,</i>

569
00:48:37,013 ---> 00:48:40,288
<i>but the survivor who is strong.</i>

570
00:48:40,289 ---> 00:48:43,531
<i>That is the way of the world!</i>

571
00:48:47,587 ---> 00:48:50,508
Were you training Jin-Yi
until this hour?

572
00:48:53,261 ---> 00:48:57,571
Everyone else left but she insisted
on staying and practicing.

573
00:48:57,701 ---> 00:49:00,041
What will you do if she wins the wager?

574
00:49:00,042 ---> 00:49:03,051
If she wins and tells you she no
longer wants to be a courtesan,

575
00:49:03,052 ---> 00:49:06,079
will you be able to handle
the disappointment?

576
00:49:06,451 ---> 00:49:08,551
I have no choice.

577
00:49:08,752 ---> 00:49:13,171
A promise is a promise.
If she wants to go, I have to let her.

578
00:49:13,793 ---> 00:49:18,208
It's been ten years! You raised
her and trained her for ten years!

579
00:49:18,209 ---> 00:49:20,169
And you're just going to let her go?

580
00:49:21,739 ---> 00:49:25,672
If it is the kind of love that
can withstand the world,

581
00:49:25,673 ---> 00:49:28,173
won't it be good if it survives?

582
00:49:28,174 ---> 00:49:30,843
How can that be possible?

583
00:49:31,443 ---> 00:49:33,913
Let's wait and see.

584
00:49:34,153 ---> 00:49:36,545
It will be good if love wins.

585
00:49:36,616 ---> 00:49:39,565
And it will be better if it does not.

586
00:49:39,665 ---> 00:49:45,435
Baik? Frankly speaking, I am more
worried about her losing the wager.

587
00:49:45,535 ---> 00:49:49,965
If she loses, can you imagine
her heartbreak and sorrow?

588
00:49:50,003 ---> 00:49:51,738
The sky will collapse
a thousand times

589
00:49:51,739 ---> 00:49:55,148
and her heart will break
into a million pieces!

590
00:49:55,149 ---> 00:49:57,868
You should never have placed
that wager with her.

591
00:49:58,048 ---> 00:49:59,727
What if she becomes like her mother...!

592
00:49:59,733 ---> 00:50:04,566
That will never happen.
She is stronger than that.

593
00:50:05,132 ---> 00:50:06,747
Art, my dear woman,

594
00:50:07,648 ---> 00:50:12,042
is a cruel tree that feeds on
the sorrow of the artist.

595
00:50:13,581 ---> 00:50:15,800
Through this one incident,

596
00:50:15,835 ---> 00:50:21,418
the Song-Do Troupe may find a rare
and exceptional prodigy in our midst.

597
00:50:36,800 ---> 00:50:38,760
A wager?

598
00:50:40,728 ---> 00:50:43,489
- How did you find out?
- Who cares how?

599
00:50:45,455 ---> 00:50:49,108
Keep it to yourself.
Don't tell anyone.

600
00:50:49,109 ---> 00:50:52,798
What is so good about love?
Does love clothe you or feed you?

601
00:50:52,799 ---> 00:50:56,775
Or does it improve your
beloved artistic talents?

602
00:50:57,835 ---> 00:51:01,855
Can you do without them?
Can you live with them?

603
00:51:02,705 ---> 00:51:04,384
Itu benar.

604
00:51:05,974 ---> 00:51:08,964
Apakah Anda gila?
Are you a fool?

605
00:51:10,324 ---> 00:51:12,372
I must be.

606
00:51:33,582 ---> 00:51:34,761
Apakah kau tidak lelah?

607
00:51:35,472 ---> 00:51:37,991
Mind your own business.

608
00:51:39,282 ---> 00:51:41,822
Home ...

609
00:51:42,804 ---> 00:51:46,144
Your mother wants you to visit home.

610
00:51:49,934 ---> 00:51:52,384
Did you go to my house again?

611
00:51:53,694 ---> 00:51:56,914
Who are you to go to my
house everyday!

612
00:51:58,584 ---> 00:52:01,934
Jangan pergi. From now on, don't even
let your shadow near my house.

613
00:52:02,974 ---> 00:52:06,804
When I raise my hair, my family will be fine
even without help from the likes of you.

614
00:52:06,805 ---> 00:52:11,621
I'm going to build them a nice house
and make them proud, you know?

615
00:52:12,148 ---> 00:52:13,908
Aku tahu.

616
00:52:15,926 ---> 00:52:21,046
Anyway, try and visit home when
Anda bisa. Your mother's very ill.

617
00:52:40,516 ---> 00:52:43,296
You are the only one I can depend on now.

618
00:52:44,586 ---> 00:52:49,746
From the day I rescued you
from the hovel of a house,

619
00:52:52,496 ---> 00:52:55,306
I knew a day like today would come.

620
00:52:57,136 ---> 00:52:59,208
Let's see what you can do.

621
00:52:59,243 ---> 00:53:04,347
Beauty and talent like yours should
lengthen my power for another ten years.

622
00:53:04,348 ---> 00:53:06,800
Apakah aku kanan?

623
00:53:12,396 ---> 00:53:15,776
Make her the loveliest of all women.

624
00:53:15,777 ---> 00:53:19,756
We must make it so there is no one
else who can compare to her.

625
00:53:21,277 ---> 00:53:25,197
That is the only way she can win the
heart of a man who is incomparable to others.

626
00:54:48,889 ---> 00:54:52,169
I think I will give you a great reward.

627
00:54:52,880 ---> 00:54:56,709
I am glad that I did not disappoint you.

628
00:54:57,549 ---> 00:55:00,880
Will a house with a tiled-roof be enough?

629
00:55:07,590 ---> 00:55:11,260
Would that not be insufficient?

630
00:55:12,960 ---> 00:55:14,930
Insufficient?

631
00:55:16,410 ---> 00:55:20,151
Then, what about a house
and a ceremonial wig?

632
00:55:29,180 ---> 00:55:31,910
I do not want that either, my Lord.

633
00:55:35,840 ---> 00:55:38,260
Lalu ...

634
00:55:41,446 ---> 00:55:44,126
I don't need anything else.

635
00:55:46,116 ---> 00:55:50,626
Give me the future of the Palace Troupe.

636
00:55:51,832 ---> 00:55:54,732
The future of the Palace Troupe?

637
00:55:55,462 ---> 00:55:58,052
That is right.

638
00:55:58,053 ---> 00:56:01,029
If your lordship so desires,

639
00:56:01,030 ---> 00:56:06,140
would it not be easier to give
than a house or a ceremonial wig?

640
00:56:17,132 ---> 00:56:22,732
I do not think that you are worthy
enough for me to raise your hair.

641
00:56:23,331 ---> 00:56:24,601
My Lord!

642
00:56:24,636 ---> 00:56:29,161
A courtesan who sells her smile and
her talents is still a courtesan after all.

643
00:56:29,902 ---> 00:56:32,391
How dare you covet power!

644
00:56:38,138 ---> 00:56:42,728
Kau tahu ...
I do not mind materialistic women,

645
00:56:43,628 ---> 00:56:47,898
but I detest women who
crave power and fame.

646
00:57:01,178 ---> 00:57:03,738
<i>Practice with all your heart.</i>

647
00:57:03,739 ---> 00:57:08,860
<i>It would be unfortunate if your
young master gave up everything</i>

648
00:57:08,861 ---> 00:57:12,822
<i>and hears from others that he did
it all for a worthless girl.</i>

649
00:57:13,830 ---> 00:57:16,720
<i>It is all up to you.</i>

650
00:57:25,920 ---> 00:57:28,390
When did Father say he would return?

651
00:57:28,591 ---> 00:57:31,100
He said he would be a while.

